  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <i>TALPA</i>! Immerse yourself in the mind of a child during a school day, when fatigue transports them into a dreamlike world where <strong>reality and imagination</strong> merge. In this bizarre inner universe, the child falls asleep, and their brain transforms into a surreal battlefield filled with fascinating moles waiting to be hit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras/67febd7600f4167a0d9e015e27371bda.avif?t=1746043800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras_big/67febd7600f4167a0d9e015e27371bda.avif?t=1746043800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your <strong>goal</strong> is simple but exciting: hit as many moles as you can with your hammer, aiming to achieve the highest score possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras/3db05d690d29f1a5f837c8f17b986180.avif?t=1746043800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras_big/3db05d690d29f1a5f837c8f17b986180.avif?t=1746043800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be careful</strong> not to miss the moles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras/bf30d823b29895b246d56d3663eb0b37.avif?t=1746043800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras_big/bf30d823b29895b246d56d3663eb0b37.avif?t=1746043800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover all the <strong>wonderful creatures</strong> that live in the game garden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras/91dd6f077d144f19f499f42d4f52973e.avif?t=1746043800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras_big/91dd6f077d144f19f499f42d4f52973e.avif?t=1746043800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't get distracted</strong> by anything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras/1f00c5e5cccdb79ae2db22ec64442250.avif?t=1746043800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras_big/1f00c5e5cccdb79ae2db22ec64442250.avif?t=1746043800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But there's a hidden twist! Discover the secret hammer that, deep inside the child's mind, transforms into the l<strong>egendary Mjöllnir</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras/524418bc3f94a5ca7105dca4c6ca0cf6.avif?t=1746043800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3585430/extras_big/524418bc3f94a5ca7105dca4c6ca0cf6.avif?t=1746043800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcomes the <strong>night</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a unique and fast-paced gaming experience where every shot counts in this epic clash between dream and reality!</p></li></ul>",
